<D>__{bill, why don't you ask her... she's your special friend.}
<A>__{a voice from upstairs answers.}
<C>__{mother}
<D>__{ain't got one.}
<A>__{mother comes into view from the darkness above. she is in her fifties, but looks younger. a sleazy white trash queen. she slowly descends the stairs.}
